import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
In [76]:
table1 = pd.read_csv("./coin.csv")    # the whole dataset
In [77]:
volume = []
date = []
In [78]:
for currency in table1['Currency'].unique().tolist():
    #print(currency)
    sub_table = table1.loc[table1['Currency'] == currency]

    sub_table_date = sub_table.loc[:,['Date']]
    sub_table_date = sub_table_date.reset_index()
    sub_table_date = sub_table_date.loc[:,['Date']]
    #print(sub_table_date)
    sub_table_volume = sub_table.loc[:,['Volume']]
    sub_table_volume = sub_table_volume.reset_index()
    sub_table_volume = sub_table_volume.loc[:,['Volume']]
    #print(sub_table_volume)

    volume.clear()
    date.clear()
    l = len(sub_table_volume)
    for _ in range(l):
        if(_%30 == 0):
            volume.append(float(sub_table_volume['Volume'][l-_-1].replace(',','')))
            date.append(str(sub_table_date['Date'][l-_-1]))
    plt.plot(date, volume, label = currency)
    
title = str("Volume (" + date[0] + " - " + date[-1] +")")
plt.title(title)
plt.legend()
plt.xticks(fontsize = 5, rotation = 75)
plt.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = [15, 8]
plt.show()

for currency in table1['Currency'].unique().tolist():
    #print(currency)
    sub_table = table1.loc[table1['Currency'] == currency]

    sub_table_date = sub_table.loc[:,['Date']]
    sub_table_date = sub_table_date.reset_index()
    sub_table_date = sub_table_date.loc[:,['Date']]
    #print(sub_table_date)
    sub_table_volume = sub_table.loc[:,['Volume']]
    sub_table_volume = sub_table_volume.reset_index()
    sub_table_volume = sub_table_volume.loc[:,['Volume']]
    #print(sub_table_volume)
    volume.clear()
    date.clear()
    for _ in range(l):
        if(str(sub_table_date['Date'][l-_-1]).endswith("2014")):
            volume.append(float(sub_table_volume['Volume'][l-_-1].replace(',','')))
            date.append(str(sub_table_date['Date'][l-_-1]))
    plt.plot(date, volume, label = currency)

title = str("Volume (" + date[0] + " - " + date[-1] +")")

plt.legend()
plt.xticks(fontsize = 5, rotation = 75)
plt.xticks([(x*15+1) for x in range(25)])
plt.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = [12, 5]
plt.show()
